    %% ============================
    %% CONEXIONES - Leyenda: --> = implementado | -.- = pendiente
    %% ============================

    Users -->|Sends Message| Meta
    GoogleAuth -->|OAuth Flow| AuthConfig
    AuthConfig -->|POST /auth/google| Auth
    LoginPage & RegisterPage -.- Users
    DashboardPage & OnboardingPage -.- OperatorRole
    
    Meta -->|Webhook Event| Webhook
    Webhook -->|Processes Data| ChatbotRouter
    Webhook -.-|Calls API| CatalogRouter
    
    ChatbotRouter -->|Internal Logic| WhatsAppService
    ChatbotRouter -->|State Management| StateManager
    WhatsAppService -->|Calls API| Meta
    
    ChatbotRouter -->|log_event()| EventLogger
    EventLogger -->|INSERT| PG
    MetricsQueries -->|SELECT| PG
    
    CatalogService -->|CRUD| PG
    CalendarService -->|CRUD| PG
    NegocioService -->|Orquestación| PG
    FAQService -->|CRUD| PG
    
    StateManager -.- Redis
    Security -.- Webhook
    Settings -.- Webhook
    Database -->|Base.metadata.create_all| PG

    %% ============================
    %% SCHEDULER CONNECTIONS
    %% ============================

    CeleryConfig -->|broker| Redis
    CeleryTasks -->|send_message| WhatsAppService
    CeleryTasks -->|SELECT turnos| PG
    CeleryTasks -->|INSERT reminder_log| PG
    CeleryTasks -->|log_event reminder_sent| EventLogger
    CeleryBeat -->|dispara cada 9 AM| CeleryTasks

    %% ============================
    %% CI/CD CONNECTIONS
    %% ============================

    CIWorkflow -.-|Runs on push| FrontendApp
    CIWorkflow -.-|Runs on push| BE

    %% ============================
    %% DEPLOYMENT CONNECTIONS
    %% ============================

    DockerCompose -->|Orquesta| APIContainer
    DockerCompose -->|Orquesta| FrontContainer
    DockerCompose -->|Orquesta| DBContainer
    DockerCompose -->|Orquesta| RedisContainer
    DockerCompose -->|Orquesta| CeleryWorker
    DockerCompose -->|Orquesta| CeleryBeat
    
    APIContainer -->|Ejecuta| Webhook
    FrontContainer -->|Sirve| FrontendApp
    DBContainer -->|Persiste datos| DBVolumen
    RedisContainer -->|Persiste datos| RedisVolumen
    
    DBContainer -.-|Backend conecta vía| PG
    RedisContainer -.-|Backend conecta vía| Redis

